description:
Primary Colours is the second full-length studio album by Canadian reggae-fusion group MAGIC! The album was released on July 1, 2016, though Latium and RCA Records worldwide. It serves as the follow-up to the band's debut studio album, Don't Kill the Magic (2014). The album was led by the single "Lay You Down Easy", featuring Sean Paul.
